.TP
.B  \-L\fP,\fB  \-\-list\-supported
list supported schemes and formats
.TP
.BI \-i\fP,\fB  \-\-input\fB= IO_URI
Input file or device URI
.TP
.BI \-\-input\-format\fB= FILE_FORMAT
